<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.2.9">
<l>eṇṭicai yumeṟi nīrkka ṭalu mēḻula kumuṭa ṉēvi ḻuṅki</l>
<l>maṇṭiyō rāli laippaḷ ḷikoḷḷum māyarkol māya maṟiya māṭṭēṉ</l>
<l>koṇṭaṉaṉ mālva raiyē yumoppar koṅkalar tāma raikkaṇ ṇumvāyum</l>
<l>aṇṭatta marar paṇiya niṉṟā raccō voruva raḻaki yavā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having gulped [and] gobbled all at once the eight regions,</l>
<l rend="indent">the sea of roiling waters,</l>
<l>And the seven worlds, is he the wonder who sleeps on a banyan leaf?</l>
<l rend="indent">I cannot understand [this] wonderment!</l>
<l>He resembles rain clouds [and] a very dark mountain;</l>
<l rend="indent">his eyes and mouth are fragrant blooming lotuses.</l>
<l>He remains [eternal] while heavenly immortals worship.</l>
<l rend="indent">Oh, the way that one is handsome!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
